      "date": "2015-11-25 06:11:33.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Could you please investigate the failure in https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/1f9a1960-79c1-11e5-9fb3-5254006e85c2\n > since that is the same script that was modified by this patch.\n\n\n > Could you please investigate the failure in https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/1f9a1960-79c1-11e5-9fb3-5254006e85c2\n > since that is the same script that was modified by this patch.\n\nFrom the test link ,didn't find test case failure related to 85b in reply-single.sh able to see test results upto test_70b only.\nfrom the logs found this info related to test_70b.\n\nonyx-31vm6:  rpc : @@@@@@ FAIL: can't put import for mdc.lustre-MDT0000-mdc-*.mds_server_uuid into FULL state after 1475 sec, have REPLAY \nonyx-31vm5:  rpc : @@@@@@ FAIL: can't put import for mdc.lustre-MDT0000-mdc-*.mds_server_uuid into FULL state after 1475 sec, have REPLAY \nreplay-single test_70b: @@@@@@ FAIL: import is not in FULL state \n\nthis patch did modification to test_85b only.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
    {
